µJEWell, having written a review of µC6Saxonia #1µC4 which was never published due to the heavy delay on µC6JP#13µC4, I decided to cut it to a short one and add a small comment for this last issue of JP as I think µC5RumrunnerµC4 and friends deserve it for what they have done, something that might save the scene (in addition to µC5Nukleus'µC6 Cows'n'Snake FightsµC4 of course). And maybe it can help to improve as I know that reaction from the readership does not reach an editor these days anymore.

This is what I feel after executing the scene's new baby µC6Saxonia:µC4 I am like thrown back in time. I feel like a child sitting in front of an A500, sitting and staring at the screen, reading a new mag. I feel like the uncool nerd I was, trying to feel like the old elite, but still being unscenish and mostly playing games any way.

